sentence: obituary for: merlien m. skjold | tomon & sons funeral home| site manager: login home obituaries about us facilities services merchandise planning a funeral pre-planning immediate arrangements grief support expressions of sympathy links obituaries merlien m. skjold (december 19, 1937 - june 10, 2015) merlien m. skjold (nee short), age 77, passed away wednesday, june 10, 2015.
beloved wife of 58 years of peter j. devoted mother of deborah (henry) jackson, peter jay, terra (tracy) bass, and patricia.
loving grandmother of angela, charlie, rebekah, stephanie, dustin, kimberly, jacob, suzanne, jesse, and steven.
great grandmother of 14. loving sister-in-law, aunt & cousin to many.
merlien was an avid bowler and a cleveland sports fanatic.

family will receive friends in the tomon & sons funeral home, 7327 pearl rd., (s. of bagley), middleburg hts., saturday, june 13, 2015 from 3-5 p. m. in lieu of flowers, donations may be made in her memory to the alzheimers association, www.
